videos.description: Allerik Freeman intercepts a pass and knocks down a 3-pointer on the other end for NC State.
videos.headline: Freeman turns steal into 3-pointer

videos.description: Terance Mann tosses up a lob to Christ Koumadje who throws down a dunk for Florida State.
videos.headline: Mann connects with Koumadje for alley-oop

videos.description: Two quick passes by NC State allows Allerik Freeman to hit an open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Good passing leads to Freeman 3-pointer

videos.description: Allerik Freeman gets another steal and takes it all the way for an NC State basket.
videos.headline: Freeman turns defense into offense and scores layup

videos.description: Braxton Beverly tosses the ball up to Omer Yurtseven, who jams it down for NC State.
videos.headline: Yurtseven dunks home lob pass

videos.description: Wolfpack use a balanced attack to ensure a rout of the 25th ranked Semioles 92-72.
videos.headline: Total team effort leads NC State to big win over Florida State
